title: Russ, Big Bank, DJ Scream - Mama I Made It!

description:
Russ joins Big Bank and DJ Scream On Big Facts to discuss his humble beginnings, the Doja Cat situation, the fate of trash talkers, Nipsey Hussle's influence and his newest project Shake The Snow Globe.
